data.description: Welcome home to this gorgeous, quiet brick ranch home that has been completely remodeled and meticulously maintained.  Your new home is centrally located 5 minutes from Harvey Park & Belmar, 15 minutes from downtown, and minutes away from 6th or HWY 285 for a trip to the mountains. The main level features ample windows and natural light throughout. As soon as you open the door you are welcomed with fantastic hardwood floors that flow throughout the entire home.  Downstairs is spacious with tall ceilings and even includes an additional kitchen which has the potential to be used as supplemental rental income or an airbnb. Supplement these crazy interest rates with some rental income!  If that's not enough you can relax and unwind in the large sunroom that features an abundance of light and new vinyl flooring. The backyard has two large storage sheds and a beautiful mature tree for shade to enjoy those beautiful Colorado days.  All of this with the luxury of no HOA!  Schedule your showing today!
